=== 2018年5月近拱點觀測 ===
2018年7月，[[赖因哈德·根策尔|赖因哈德·根策尔]]等人的論文<ref name=”aa33718-18”>[https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full_html/2018/07/aa33718-18/aa33718-18.html Detection of the gravitational redshift in the orbit of the star S2 near the Galactic centre massive black hole] {{Wayback|url=https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full_html/2018/07/aa33718-18/aa33718-18.html |date=20190404120522 }}, Genzel et al, [[天文与天体物理学报|Astronomy & Astrophysics]], DOI [[doi:10.1051/0004-6361/201833718|doi:10.1051/0004-6361/201833718]], 2018-07-26</ref><ref name=”2017-07-26_TG”>[https://www.theguardian.com/science/2018/jul/26/star-spotted-speeding-near-milky-way-black-hole-for-first-time Star spotted speeding near black hole at centre of Milky Way -- Chile’s Very Large Telescope tracks S2 star as it reaches mind-boggling speeds by supermassive black hole] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2018/jul/26/star-spotted-speeding-near-milky-way-black-hole-for-first-time |date=20190404100253 }}, [[衛報|The Guardian]], 2017-07-26</ref>中報告，S2的軌道速度於同年5月位於距離人馬座A*約120天文單位（相當於人馬座A*的1400倍[[史瓦西半徑|史瓦西半徑]]）的[[拱點|近拱點]]時達到了7650 km/s，相當於光速的2.55%。這讓該組天文學家斷言S2[[狭义相对论|在接近相對論速度]]的[[紅移|紅移]]，尤其是[[廣義相對論|廣義相對論]]的[[重力紅移|重力紅移]]被確認。

== S0–102 ==
{{main|S0-102}}
2012年，天文學家發現另一顆比S2更接近銀河系中心超大質量黑洞的恆星[[S0-102|S0-102]]。S0-102的亮度只有S2的十六分之一，因此天文學家無法立即確認，而是累積多年觀測資料才將該恆星的光從該天區背景紅外光中分離。S0-102的軌道週期是比S2更短的11.5年。在圍繞銀河系中心黑洞的恆星中只有S2和S0-102在三維空間的軌道參數和軌跡是完全已知的<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Meyer | first1 = L. | last2 = Ghez | first2 = A. M. | last3 = Schödel | first3 = R. | last4 = Yelda | first4 = S. | last5 = Boehle | first5 = A. | last6 = Lu | first6 = J. R. | last7 = Do | first7 = T. | last8 = Morris | first8 = M. R. | last9 = Becklin | first9 = E. E. | last10 = Matthews | first10 = K. | doi = 10.1126/science.1225506 | title = The Shortest-Known-Period Star Orbiting Our Galaxy's Supermassive Black Hole | journal = Science | volume = 338 | issue = 6103 | pages = 84–87 | year = 2012 | pmid =  23042888| pmc = |arxiv = 1210.1294 |bibcode = 2012Sci...338...84M }}</ref>。對天文學家來說，發現2顆極為靠近銀河系中心超大質量黑洞的恆星是相當有趣的，因為天文學家將可同時使用這兩顆恆星的觀測資料，得到比只使用S2資料更精確的黑洞周圍重力性質與廣義相對論量測結果{{cn|date=July 2018}}。

